💕 TRACKING SHOWS ARRIVED
There’s not a whole lot we can do when the tracking info shows it as being delivered. Please check with everyone in your household as someone else might have brought it in. Sometimes we have heard of a package going to a neighbor mistakenly or being left at a different/side door. In our experience, usually the package is located.
Most orders are shipped via UPS Mail Innovations or UPS Surepost, and final delivery is by the USPS so we also suggest having the customer contact their local post office and many times they can get in touch with the actual person who delivered it and see if they recall where they left it. 💕 NO TRACKING OR NO MOVEMENT
If a package does not show any movement and has passed the allotted time for delivery we will send a new package at our cost to the customer.  We may ask you to check to very the address or supply us with a new shipping address.
SIZING EXCHANGE
We don't offer exchanges or refunds in those situations.
💕 PRODUCT ISSUE
If it is an issue on our end where we sent out the wrong product, wrong size, bad graphic just send us a picture of what you have  received for quality control purposes and we can offer a refund or replacement once the issue is deemed our fault.
US customers have up to 30 days after the shipped date and international customers have up to 60 days after the shipped date.
What we need to make a replacement order:
1.	Please provide the name and email.
2.	Please provide the order number.
3.	Please provide picture of wrong/ damaged item And Shipping Label.

results.title: Live Love Laugh Butterfly on Pink Shabby Chic Background Purse Hook Bag Hanger Lipstick Compact Mirror
results.description:
Live Love Laugh Butterfly on Pink Shabby Chic Background Foldable Purse Hook Bag Hanger Lipstick Compact Mirror - Printed on Pearl Metallic Paper
 
This listing is for a foldable purse hook / bag hanger with a double-sided compact mirror and features the inspirational words live love laugh on a shabby chic pink textured background with a white butterfly silhouette.

Purse hooks are stylish and a practical solution to the dilemna women face when they go out of where to put their handbags. The floor is dirty and not sanitary. It's socially impolite to put your bag on the table. Every woman could use a purse hook mirror and a  way to check their lipstick. It is very easily to use.

This is the highest quality purse hook mirror available... Here are some details:

Large image area for art, graphics and photos that is approx. 30mm or 1 3/16 inch in diameter.  

The purse hanger folded is approx 1 7/8 inch in diameter and supports up to 20 pounds.  

The back has a special striped non-slip pad to protect table surfaces.  

It's lead-free and nickel-free and fully complies with RICH standards and PRO test California 65.  

This purse hanger is silver toned with thick plating and has a highly polished perfect finish with stainless steel hinges so it's very durable as well as corrosion and water-resistant. 

It has magnetic closures for both the foldable part of the purse hook and compact mirror. 

Packaged in a small black velvet pouch.

Images are printed on pearl metallic paper using an Epson R2880 pigment ink printer and then protected with transparent epoxy resin domes. This Epson printer is used by many professional photographers and artists and boasts archival quality.

Graphics and photographs print beautifully on the pearl metallic paper. There is a richness and depth to the image and it has an iridescence that is lovely and unmatched by printing on regular paper or even photo paper.

If you have any questions, please let me know. I'm skilled with graphics so if you have artwork or photos or a different idea that you would like for a design, please get in touch with me. Most designs can be personalized by request for no charge.

The digital collage graphics for this love themed purse hook mirror were purchased on etsy at http://designsbylindanee.etsy.com  She has some great graphics so please feel free to visit her shop. If you see anything that you would love to have made into a purse hook mirror or any of the items I make, just let me know.

Please feel free to visit my other etsy shops...almost any design in either of these shops can be made into a purse hook mirror.
